\f2\b \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 digital billboard network hidden inside a 24/7 lo-fi stream
\f1\b0 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 . Brands can pay you to take over a storefront for a week or a month, allowing you to update the stream seamlessly without turning it off.\
To achieve a 24/7 continuous stream that updates seamlessly on the fly, you 
\f2\b \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 cannot
\f1\b0 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774  upload 6-hour video files manually [1]. You must run a 24/7 server using a tool like OBS Studio or FFmpeg to stream directly to YouTube via a stream key.\
Here is how to update the code to handle precise structural time triggers and dynamic brand swap-outs.\
