\f0\b\fs42 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 \cf0 1. Updated Python Script: Structural Triggers & Ad Injection\
\pard\pardeftab560\slleading80\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 \cf0 This updated code uses a dictionary-based asset manager. To change a storefront brand for a real advertiser, you simply drop a new PNG image into your 
\fs28\fsmilli14118 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 ads/
